comments: Tethered a giant robot dinosaur to the ground with a cool sci-fi harpoon launcher, show a giant machine gun off of its head with a bow and arrow, and then used its own head-machine-gun to blow it up. 10/10.
Snuck around in some grass and shot evil people in the head.
Had to walk through a half-hour long dungeon listening to plot exposition via overlong audio logs instead of actually playing the game.
